  • Uses of ResultSetMetaData in java.sql

    Methods in java.sql that return ResultSetMetaData 
    Modifier and Type Method Description
    ResultSetMetaData PreparedStatement.getMetaData()
    Retrieves a ResultSetMetaData object that contains information about the columns of the ResultSet object that will be returned when this PreparedStatement object is executed.
    ResultSetMetaData ResultSet.getMetaData()
    Retrieves the number, types and properties of this ResultSet object's columns.

    interface  RowSetMetaData

    Classes in javax.sql.rowset that implement ResultSetMetaData 
    Modifier and Type Class Description
